description: Retrieves the specified registration attachments or all registration attachments associated with your Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: RegistrationAttachmentIds
parameters.description: The unique identifier of registration attachments to find. This is an array of RegistrationAttachmentId. (string) ---

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: An array of RegistrationAttachmentFilter objects to filter the results. (dict) --- The filter definition for filtering registration attachments that meets a specified criteria. The name of the attribute to filter on. An array of values to filter on. (string) ---

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the attribute to filter on.

nested_params.name: Values
nested_params.description: An array of values to filter on.

nested_items.name: RegistrationAttachmentArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the registration attachment.

nested_items.name: RegistrationAttachmentId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the registration attachment.

nested_items.name: AttachmentStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the registration attachment.
UPLOAD_IN_PROGRESS The attachment is being uploaded.
UPLOAD_COMPLETE The attachment has been uploaded.
UPLOAD_FAILED The attachment failed to uploaded.
DELETED The attachment has been deleted..

nested_items.name: AttachmentUploadErrorReason
nested_items.description: A description of why the upload didn't successfully complete.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The time when the registration attachment was created, in UNIX epoch time format.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to be used for the next set of paginated results. You don't need to supply a value for this field in the initial request.
